
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Sunrise Financial — Sample</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Merriweather:wght@400;700&family=Open+Sans:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; color: #2c2c2c; background: #fff; }
    nav { background: #fff; border-bottom: 2px solid #e07b2a; padding: 0 40px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; height: 64px; }
    .nav-logo { font-family: 'Merriweather', serif; font-size: 20px; color: #e07b2a; font-weight: 700; }
    .nav-logo span { color: #333; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 28px; }
    .nav-links a { color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: #e07b2a; }
    .hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff8f0 0%, #fff3e0 100%); padding: 80px 40px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0d8b0; }
    .hero-tag { display: inline-block; background: #e07b2a22; color: #e07b2a; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px; border: 1px solid #e07b2a44; }
    .hero h1 { font-family: 'Merriweather', serif; font-size: 42px; line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #2c1810; max-width: 660px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
    .hero p { font-size: 17px; color: #7a5540; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 36px; line-height: 1.7; font-weight: 300; }
    .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn-primary { background: #e07b2a; color: white; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.2s; }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: #c06820; }
    .btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: #e07b2a; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 15px; border: 1px solid #e07b2a; text-decoration: none; }
    .section { padding: 72px 40px; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .section-tag { font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #e07b2a; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 600; }
    .section h2 { font-family: 'Merriweather', serif; font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #2c1810; }
    .section-sub { font-size: 16px; color: #7a5540; max-width: 560px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
    .card { border: 1px solid #f0d8b0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 28px; transition: box-shadow 0.2s; }
    .card:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(224,123,42,0.12); }
    .card-icon { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .card h3 { font-family: 'Merriweather', serif; font-size: 17px; color: #2c1810; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .card p { font-size: 14px; color: #7a5540; line-height: 1.7; }
    .rita-banner { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3e0 0%, #fff8f0 100%); border-top: 1px solid #f0d8b0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0d8b0; padding: 56px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .rita-banner h2 { font-family: 'Merriweather', serif; font-size: 30px; color: #2c1810; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .rita-banner p { font-size: 16px; color: #7a5540; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto 28px; line-height: 1.7; }
    .rita-banner-btn { background: #e07b2a; color: white; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; border: none; cursor: pointer; }
    footer { background: #2c1810; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); padding: 32px 40px; text-align: center; font-size: 13px; }
    footer span { color: #e07b2a; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .hero h1 { font-size: 30px; } .nav-links { display: none; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav>
    <div class="nav-logo">Sunrise <span>Financial</span></div>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#">Planning</a><a href="#">Retirement</a><a href="#">Our Team</a><a href="#">Contact</a>
    </div>
  </nav>
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-tag">Your Retirement Partners</div>
    <h1>A Brighter Retirement Starts Here</h1>
    <p>We help you build financial confidence and a life full of meaning in your retirement years.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#" class="btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation</a>
      <a href="#" class="btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-tag">Our Services</div>
    <h2>Planning for the Whole Retirement</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Financial security matters — and so does how you spend your days. We help with both.</p>
    <div class="cards">
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">☀️</div><h3>Income Planning</h3><p>Structure your savings to generate reliable, sustainable income throughout retirement.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🌿</div><h3>Lifestyle Coaching</h3><p>Find purpose, routine, and joy in the non-financial side of your retirement transition.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🏡</div><h3>Estate Planning</h3><p>Protect your legacy and ensure your wishes are honored for the people you love.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="rita-banner">
    <h2>Questions About Retirement Life?</h2>
    <p>RITA is our AI retirement lifestyle assistant — available 24/7 to help with anything on your mind.</p>
    <button class="rita-banner-btn" onclick="document.getElementById('rita-fab').click()">Ask RITA →</button>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-tag">Sample Page</div>
    <h2>This is a Demo</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">This page demonstrates how the RITA™ widget looks on a warm, orange-branded financial advisory website. Notice the widget in the bottom right matches the Sunrise Financial color scheme.</p>
  </div>
  <footer><p>© 2026 Sunrise Financial, LLC · <span>Sample demonstration page</span> · Powered by RITA™ from Third Act Advisors</p></footer>
  <script src="https://darling-dragon-f1fb92.netlify.app/assets/rita-widget.js?client=sunrise"></script>
</body>
</html>
